# Task Tool Subagent Description Convention

When using the Task tool, prefix the `description` parameter with the subagent type in brackets for UI clarity.

## Format

```
description: "[subagent_type] Brief description of task"
```

## Examples

```
✅ "[search-agent] Analyze authentication flow"
✅ "[generalPurpose] Refactor database queries"
✅ "[best-of-n-runner] Test migration approach"
✅ "[cursor-guide] Find docs on MCP setup"

❌ "Analyze authentication flow"  (missing type prefix)
```

This helps identify which specialized subagent is running in the CLI output:

```
⬢ 1 agent completed
  [search-agent] Analyze authentication flow
  ✓ Done
```
